@startuml
title UC01 Credential owner が provider credential を登録する

actor "Credential owner" as Owner
participant "Enki Gate UI" as UI
participant "Enki Gate API" as API
participant "Upstream provider" as Provider
database "Firestore" as Firestore
collections "Cloud KMS" as KMS

Owner -> UI: credential 登録画面を開く
UI --> Owner: provider 選択と API key 入力フォームを表示

Owner -> UI: provider と API key を入力して送信
UI -> API: credential 登録を要求
API -> Provider: API key の妥当性を確認
Provider --> API: 妥当性確認結果

alt API key が有効
  API -> KMS: 暗号化に必要な鍵処理を要求
  KMS --> API: 暗号化に必要な結果
  API -> Firestore: ciphertext と metadata を保存
  Firestore --> API: 保存完了
  API --> UI: 登録成功
  UI --> Owner: 登録完了を表示
else API key が無効
  API --> UI: 登録失敗
  UI --> Owner: エラーを表示
end
@enduml
